STATNAME:Constitution	SORTKEY:3	ABB:CON	KEY:CON	STATMOD:floor(SCORE/2)-5	DEFINE:MAXLEVELSTAT=CON|CONSCORE-10		BONUS:HP|CURRENTMAX|-TL		DEFINE:HealingSurges|0	BONUS:VAR|HealingSurges|CON	DEFINE:BloodiedValue|0	BONUS:VAR|BloodiedValue|HP/2	DEFINE:HealingSurgeValue|0	BONUS:VAR|HealingSurgeValue|HP/4
